# MarkNote Demo!
Welcome to the MarkNote Demo! Here you can see all the different thins you can do with MarkNote!

MarkNote uses Markdown which is a unique document language that can easily be converted to HTML for better viewing. MarkNote takes markdown to the next level by adding features, and endless possibilities.


## This page is 100% editable!

Feel free to change the text here! Keep in mind this demo is limited by the text editor, saving, and opening files are disabled.


## Click around!
Feel free to check out the information panels (left on desktop / tablet and top for mobile)! MarkNote includes information on markdown formatting!


## Include Images!

Images can be included in markdown by URL only (there will be a way to upload via google drive soon). Click the image to see the syntax!

![img](https://marknote.ue.r.appspot.com/public/images/MarkNote%20-%20Editor.png)

You can also embed SVG images if they are in a URL format! This works very well when using diagrams.net!

![svg](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)
